==English==

===Etymology===
Originally in plural from French [[orgies]], from Latin [[orgia]] (neuter plural) cognate with Greek [[οργια]], both meaning ‘secret rites, revels’.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|org|y}}

# A [[revel]] involving [[indiscriminate]] sexual activity.
# Excessive [[indulgence]] in a specified activity.

